| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3795 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8c0eb809-2644-5f43-9fca-9eebb72bb4ec"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
